<TITLE> RAB arrests 1 for having gun </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Apr 29 (bdnews24.com)  RAB arrested a man for possession of an illegal firearm from Dhaka's Shekhertek on Thursday. A statement from Rapid Action Battalion-1 assistant director Mohammad Zahirul Islam said that Md Mizanur Rahman, 32, was arrested from a housing society at Shekhertek. A foreign revolver and three rounds of bullets were recovered from him. The arrested has long been carrying out criminal activities like robberies, muggings and murders at Dhaka's Adabar, Mohammadpur and Darul Salam areas. The statement said that Mizanur confessed to these crimes during interrogation. It also said the legal measures were underway. b
